data.description: Majestic Mountain Views from the patio of this charming 3 Bedroom Ranch with original wood floors in Bedrooms and Living room, oversized 1 Car attached Garage. 720 sq.ft 3 Car Detached Garage/Shop plus Carport. Plenty of space for RV/Boat Parking on this 1.42 acre property is suitable for 1 Horse and/or other Animals. Loafing shed with Tack room or work shop is 719 sq.ft. Large Gardent Area and Chicken Coup. Perfect Home to make your own and watch the fantastic Rocky Mountain Sunsets. Mature Trees and landscaping. Close to Hwy 287 for easy access to the Northern Front Range
